---
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-container">
		<div class="footer-grid">
			<div class="footer-brand">
				<span class="brand-name">{SITE_TITLE}</span>
				<p>현대적인 부동산 전문가를 위한 정밀 분석. 대한민국 부동산 시장의 데이터 기반 분석 및 투자 전략.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-section">
				<h5 class="label-md">주요 리소스</h5>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="/blog">시장 데이터</a></li>
					<li><a href="/blog">연구 방법론</a></li>
					<li><a href="/about">분석가 디렉토리</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-section">
				<h5 class="label-md">법적 고지</h5>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="#">이용 약관</a></li>
					<li><a href="#">개인정보 처리방침</a></li>
					<li><a href="/about">문의하기</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-section">
				<h5 class="label-md">팔로우</h5>
				<div class="social-icons">
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined">public</span>
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined">work</span>
					<span class="material-symbols-outlined">rss_feed</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-bottom">
			<p>&copy; {today.getFullYear()} {SITE_TITLE}. 전문 투자자를 위한 기관급 데이터 제공.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	footer {
		width: 100%;
		background: var(--surface-container-highest);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
		padding: 48px var(--gutter);
		margin-top: var(--stack-lg);
	}
	.footer-container {
		max-width: var(--container-max);
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.footer-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 48px;
		margin-bottom: 48px;
	}
	.brand-name {
		font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
		font-size: 24px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--primary);
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}
	.footer-brand p {
		font-size: 14px;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--on-surface-variant);
		max-width: 320px;
	}
	h5 {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--primary);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}
	ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}
	ul li {
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}
	ul li a {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: var(--on-surface-variant);
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	ul li a:hover {
		color: var(--secondary);
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.social-icons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 16px;
		color: var(--on-surface-variant);
	}
	.social-icons span {
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	.social-icons span:hover {
		color: var(--secondary);
	}
	.footer-bottom {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
		padding-top: 32px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.footer-bottom p {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: var(--on-surface-variant);
	}
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		}
	}
	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.footer-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 32px;
		}
	}
</style>
